{"tid":936110,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"互動故《島國經營模擬器》","createTime":"2018-12-10T13:42:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T15:22:40.000Z","uid":96983,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"951bf919c71d119de2ced3de7615faf294c4dc17","tid":936110,"uid":96983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T13:42:37.000Z","msg":"萬物歷 448年5月第四周<br />\n<br />\n「咁多位選民你地好，好高興可以擊敗咁多位有質素嘅選手，當選依個遠洋小島嘅領袖。<br />\n<br />\n貴為首位女性領袖，我必定會歇盡所能，為大家帶黎一個番新氣象。<br />\n<br />\n競選嘅口號唔係空口說白話。起不久嘅將來，我會一一為大家實現。<br />\n<br />\n我地嘅目標係成為世界其中一個<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>大國</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n地方雖小，但包唔住我地壯大嘅志氣，為左我地嘅未來，大家一齊努力！！」<br />\n<br />\n「好！」<br />\n<br />\n「講得好！！」<br />\n<br />\n在全場鵝們的歡呼和拍掌聲下，我回到了島國領袖辦公室。<br />\n<br />\n我係奠悅鵝，今年10歲，以鵝嘅平均壽命40年黎講我其實都只係過左四分一，可以話係非常年輕。<br />\n<br />\n有時都唔知點解佢地會揀我，不過當選左就要努力，我唔會辜負咁多位鵝民嘅期望。<br />\n<br />\n我翻看桌上嘅文件，上任嘅第一道決策就係移島，移去大國附近&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n到底我應該移去邊到好?<br />\n<br />\n賢內助，你黎得啱時間啦，到底我應該移去邊個區呢?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mCKB8Ax.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmCKB8Ax.jpg&h=6c735ab2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上、下、左、右，最快三個回覆"},{"pid":"38e88c1b716531c7132af75638e48ab2f0989156","tid":936110,"uid":161685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"951bf919c71d119de2ced3de7615faf294c4dc17","tid":936110,"uid":96983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T13:42:37.000Z","msg":"萬物歷 448年5月第四周<br />\n<br />\n「咁多位選民你地好，好高興可以擊敗咁多位有質素嘅選手，當選依個遠洋小島嘅領袖。<br />\n<br />\n貴為首位女性領袖，我必定會歇盡所能，為大家帶黎一個番新氣象。<br />\n<br />\n競選嘅口號唔係空口說白話。起不久嘅將來，我會一一為大家實現。<br />\n<br />\n我地嘅目標係成為世界其中一個<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>大國</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n地方雖小，但包唔住我地壯大嘅志氣，為左我地嘅未來，大家一齊努力！！」<br />\n<br />\n「好！」<br />\n<br />\n「講得好！！」<br />\n<br />\n在全場鵝們的歡呼和拍掌聲下，我回到了島國領袖辦公室。<br />\n<br />\n我係奠悅鵝，今年10歲，以鵝嘅平均壽命40年黎講我其實都只係過左四分一，可以話係非常年輕。<br />\n<br />\n有時都唔知點解佢地會揀我，不過當選左就要努力，我唔會辜負咁多位鵝民嘅期望。<br />\n<br />\n我翻看桌上嘅文件，上任嘅第一道決策就係移島，移去大國附近&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n到底我應該移去邊到好?<br />\n<br />\n賢內助，你黎得啱時間啦，到底我應該移去邊個區呢?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mCKB8Ax.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmCKB8Ax.jpg&h=6c735ab2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上、下、左、右，最快三個回覆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T13:45:06.000Z","msg":"右"},{"pid":"35da818a7c1342b40d1f794760fa61ed0d23d230","tid":936110,"uid":89808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T13:45:21.000Z","msg":"上"},{"pid":"1baea081cc829c3f88d05b836702aa65256ec2e9","tid":936110,"uid":139187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T13:46:12.000Z","msg":"下"},{"pid":"821b091fffed674ccbc07ffedb646de1162ca355","tid":936110,"uid":85574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T13:46:35.000Z","msg":"左"},{"pid":"cd8a71c7a7c1d7daf6bd20e4812c9c756d019cce","tid":936110,"uid":96983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T13:46:58.000Z","msg":"冇共識？起點好重要咖"},{"pid":"2630a7c25e6a81b884b5e210df2f7c29c86708d1","tid":936110,"uid":12435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T13:47:56.000Z","msg":"右"},{"pid":"6e40fcb9342ec5d4e0f513e75d483a675553b2ef","tid":936110,"uid":191812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T13:48:35.000Z","msg":"毒島"},{"pid":"4ae38cc7d1c06c51e8b334ec9581d0c2a38c786b","tid":936110,"uid":128160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T13:49:20.000Z","msg":"左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b9693b934d9e8271c9758f72f14839ae4c139e1","tid":936110,"uid":96983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T13:50:11.000Z","msg":"左定右呢"},{"pid":"bbc341de6c3f56da0e2c1813de43af9861e9019a","tid":936110,"uid":139187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T13:51:59.000Z","msg":"右"},{"pid":"4f34cf7ff0419c1d55f1c37244d9c19bef33b47e","tid":936110,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T13:54:10.000Z","msg":"上"},{"pid":"df6d695550e13e71991bcb35d576a8b16e181ff2","tid":936110,"uid":96983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:07:23.000Z","msg":"萬物歷 448年6月第一周<br />\n<br />\n嗯，雖然意見不一，但似乎比較多人揀鷹國同米國之間，一於就聽前輩嘅意見，移去個到啦。<br />\n<br />\n經過一星期嘅大遷移，我地遠洋小島終於由世界嘅邊緣移到依個位置。我地終於唔洗做邊緣鵝了！<br />\n<br />\n咦&hellip;?等等!<br />\n<br />\n立足大國左右，我地要點介紹自己呢？冇理由話自己係遠洋小島掛，我諗我地要改個新名先。<br />\n<br />\n等我諗下再俾鵝民揀:<br />\n香江<br />\n香城<br />\n香島<br />\n鵝國<br />\n唔改名<br />\n<br />\n咁多位，我地小島改做咩名好啊？四揀一，最快三位"},{"pid":"b7f340d83772c67a1cf48fc93bd722da430c1d11","tid":936110,"uid":149655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:10:51.000Z","msg":"無名島"},{"pid":"b75b2d75f92a0d4ec92cdd38164b057490287c24","tid":936110,"uid":96983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:12:47.000Z","msg":"仲有冇人啊？小弟打字慢，唔好走啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d209d1fc9707af7ff97e77166c3d5632f937da6","tid":936110,"uid":224967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b75b2d75f92a0d4ec92cdd38164b057490287c24","tid":936110,"uid":96983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:12:47.000Z","msg":"仲有冇人啊？小弟打字慢，唔好走啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:16:41.000Z","msg":"２０７元"},{"pid":"d23083c265ffcc4a5e9823f5ba2b3346e627f67a","tid":936110,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:18:15.000Z","msg":"唔改，島國"},{"pid":"de1911ced72072b61549ad421cad0b253d444006","tid":936110,"uid":96983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d209d1fc9707af7ff97e77166c3d5632f937da6","tid":936110,"uid":224967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b75b2d75f92a0d4ec92cdd38164b057490287c24","tid":936110,"uid":96983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:12:47.000Z","msg":"仲有冇人啊？小弟打字慢，唔好走啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:16:41.000Z","msg":"２０７元"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:18:29.000Z","msg":"墨巴大駕光臨，但我唔明咩點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca9972ed177095a19893060da2c0464471446218","tid":936110,"uid":96983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d23083c265ffcc4a5e9823f5ba2b3346e627f67a","tid":936110,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:18:15.000Z","msg":"唔改，島國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:20:06.000Z","msg":"唔改有一個"},{"pid":"61b1de5b0d626051306400496a45624099773530","tid":936110,"uid":96983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:26:57.000Z","msg":"萬物歷 448年6月第二周<br />\n國家狀態: 132名民眾，滿意度:100%，國庫100萬。<br />\n<br />\n咁多位鵝民似乎都好滿意依個位置同埋島國依個國家名，暫時未見有咩反對聲音。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NFu24p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNFu24p4.jpg&h=9e27e0f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我地咁多年都風平浪靜，我發現原來其他國家都有一啲叫做基礎建設嘅建築，我地都無，不如我地起一個基建先啦。<br />\n<br />\n(基建起將來故事有用)<br />\n警察局<br />\n消防局<br />\n醫院<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n賢內助我地應該起邊個好?"},{"pid":"633ef1fcbb11051d0e0bb00375b3315956eb7b84","tid":936110,"uid":96983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61b1de5b0d626051306400496a45624099773530","tid":936110,"uid":96983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:26:57.000Z","msg":"萬物歷 448年6月第二周<br />\n國家狀態: 132名民眾，滿意度:100%，國庫100萬。<br />\n<br />\n咁多位鵝民似乎都好滿意依個位置同埋島國依個國家名，暫時未見有咩反對聲音。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NFu24p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNFu24p4.jpg&h=9e27e0f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我地咁多年都風平浪靜，我發現原來其他國家都有一啲叫做基礎建設嘅建築，我地都無，不如我地起一個基建先啦。<br />\n<br />\n(基建起將來故事有用)<br />\n警察局<br />\n消防局<br />\n醫院<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n賢內助我地應該起邊個好?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:29:01.000Z","msg":"各自為10萬，最快個位。"},{"pid":"e1abe68da444263d0553858e8ee8f60abdb7435c","tid":936110,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:35:55.000Z","msg":"醫院"},{"pid":"b773ce704f7390c0e296880b3814e4be8abc461a","tid":936110,"uid":16468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:38:51.000Z","msg":"醫院"},{"pid":"d6b2e7923d5c812f1049b00a3274f580d9114cd7","tid":936110,"uid":96983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:42:53.000Z","msg":"萬物歷 448年6月第三周<br />\n國家狀態: 134名民眾，滿意度:100%，國庫90萬。<br />\n<br />\n經過多位日夜交接，鵝不停掌嘅工作之後，一間醫院終於落成。(-10萬)<br />\n<br />\n真係唔敢相信原來遷島可以令大家咁有熱誠，可以為我地國家負出自己嘅休息時間。<br />\n<br />\n醫院雖小，但五臟俱全，希望將來唔會有疾病，發揮唔到作用啦。<br />\n<br />\n到底我地要為醫院改咩名好呢？<br />\n<br />\n最快嘅賢內助，可以為醫院命名。"},{"pid":"d63b2873812de43d5c1809308e3af20fa5f77c0d","tid":936110,"uid":16468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:45:35.000Z","msg":"吳依仁醫院"}]}